	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />When you build your own development cartridge, you can substitute in RAM for ROM.  Using RAM makes it easier to link with a computer and send new code to the cartridge.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
